---

These headers are a clean-room implementation of the VST2 binary Application
Binary Interface (ABI). They are not derived from Steinberg's source code.
The VST2 binary interface specification is a factual description of a
communication protocol between audio plugins and hosts, and is not itself
subject to copyright protection.

Struct field layouts were verified for binary compatibility against
Xaymar/vst2sdk (BSD-3-Clause, https://github.com/Xaymar/vst2sdk), an
independent clean-room reverse-engineered SDK.

"VST" is a trademark of Steinberg Media Technologies GmbH. This project
makes no claim to VST trademark rights and is not endorsed by Steinberg.
